<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="arial" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span></font><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>Thank you for getting in touch with Kingsbridge.<br></span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Please accept this email as confirmation that we have removed your policy from our automatic renewal system.&nbsp;</span></font><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Your current policy is due to expire on&nbsp;</b><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>{!Opportunity.Renewal_Date__c}</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.</span></font><br></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>We’ll send automated emails to make sure you’re aware of your policy expiry date so that you can either renew your policy with us manually or find cover elsewhere to keep your business protected against claims.<br></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>Our renewals team may still get in touch to check whether your circumstances have changed, and to see if you would like to renew your policy manually.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to get in touch.<br></span><font face="arial" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span></font><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
